TEXT.TITLE: PRE-PAID LEGAL <PD> ENTERS WASHINGTON MARKET
TEXT.BODY: Pre-Paid Legal Services Inc said it will start marketing its Pre-Paid Legal Services contract in the state of Washington today. It said it is now doing business in 23 states. Reuter
